67af0ced1ee9a4724","tid":540312,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:36:34.000Z","msg":"理撚得班廢中咩，佢地其實係香港上係唔多數，只不過佢地好得閑成日上網先令到你覺得佢地周圍都係咁。事實上香港有好多知識份子同中產睇嘢係好中立"},{"pid":"8a2380725796bd6a0afd7febb0c192c8e53ee299","tid":540312,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0383426d828d1e693589ea95a027a245685fe56f","tid":540312,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ffbec5eb0c0d324564602ed5b56dec236bf3505","tid":540312,"uid":18559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係咁 食餐飯想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"同佢講，再嘈你第日自己去執紙皮，睇下仲敢唔敢出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"貴國唔收低端紙皮，敬請注意"}]}